    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Nor will I keep you longer in suspense.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "mrs Fortescue owns, what every body knows, 'that he is notoriously, nay, avowedly, a man of pleasure; yet says, that in any thing he sets his heart upon or undertakes, he is the most industrious and persevering mortal under the sun",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "He rests it seems not above six hours in the twenty four-any more than you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "He delights in writing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "'He had once it seems the vanity, upon being complimented on these talents (and on his surprising diligence, for a man of pleasure) to compare himself to Julius Caesar; who performed great actions by day, and wrote them down at night; and valued himself, that he only wanted Caesar's out setting, to make a figure among his contemporaries.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "But supposing it to be true that all his vacant nightly hours are employed in writing, what can be his subjects?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "That you and I, my dear, should love to write, is no wonder.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "We have always, from the time each could hold a pen, delighted in epistolary correspondencies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Whatever his other vices are, all the world, as well as mrs Fortescue, says, 'he is a sober man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "And among all his bad qualities, gaming, that great waster of time as well as fortune, is not his vice:' So that he must have his head as cool, and his reason as clear, as the prime of youth and his natural gaiety will permit; and by his early morning hours, a great portion of time upon his hands to employ in writing, or worse.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Both very bad and threatening indications; since the first must shew him to be utterly abandoned; and it is but natural to conclude from the other, that what a man is not ashamed to have imputed to him, he will not scruple to be guilty of whenever he has an opportunity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Upon the whole, and upon all I could gather from mrs Fortescue, mr Lovelace is a very faulty man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Nor has he complaisance enough to spare your uncles.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "His vanity would be your clue.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Talk of the devil, is an old saying.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "The lively wretch has made me a visit, and is but just gone away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I told him, that this was very hard upon him; and the more so, as neither his life nor morals perhaps would stand a fair inquiry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "He smiled, and called himself my servant.--The occasion was too fair, he said, for Miss Howe, who never spared him, to let it pass.--But, Lord help the shallow souls of the Harlowes!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Would I believe it! they were for turning plotters upon him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I asked him, If he valued himself upon having a head better turned than theirs for such works, as he called them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "He drew off: and then ran into the highest professions of reverence and affection for you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156073_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156073/2526_156073_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "The object so meritorious, who can doubt the reality of his professions?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "LETTER fifteen",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I have both your letters at once.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "That these presumers appear not in this very unworthy light to some of your friends, is, because their defects are not so striking to them as to others.--And why?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Hence your Symmes's, your Byron's, your Mullins's, your Wyerley's (the best of the herd), and your Solmes's, in turn, invade you-Wretches that, looking upon the rest of your family, need not despair of succeeding in an alliance with it-But to you, what an inexcusable presumption!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Yet I am afraid all opposition will be in vain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "You must, you will, I doubt, be sacrificed to this odious man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I know your family.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Bell has a meanness in her very pride; that meanness rises with her pride, and goes hand in hand with it; and no one is so proud as Bell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "She has owned her love, her uneasy days, and sleepless nights, and her revenge grafted upon her love, to her favourite Betty Barnes-To lay herself in the power of a servant's tongue!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Poor creature!--But LIKE little souls will find one another out, and mingle, as well as LIKE great ones.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I am too sure) that they will subdue such a fine spirit as yours, unused to opposition; and (tell it not in Gath) you must be mrs Solmes!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I know your dutiful, your laudable motives; and one would have thought, that you might have trusted to a father who so dearly loved you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "He has qualities, in short, that may make him a tolerable creature on the other side of fifty: but God help the poor woman to whose lot he shall fall till then!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156076_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156076/2526_156076_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I long for your next letter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "MISS HOWE, TO MISS CLARISSA HARLOWE.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "sunday march nineteenth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I beg your pardon, my dearest friend, for having given you occasion to remind me of the date of my last.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I was willing to have before me as much of the workings of your wise relations as possible; being verily persuaded, that one side or the other would have yielded by this time: and then I should have had some degree of certainty to found my observations upon.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "You cannot bear the thoughts of having their Solmes: and Lovelace is resolved you shall be his, let who will say to the contrary.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000008_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000008_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Let us see what their next step will be.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "But let it-if it must be Lovelace or Solmes, the choice cannot admit of debate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "But who can be worthy of a Clarissa?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "I must own, that I should think myself inexcusable so to do, (the rather, as I am bold enough to imagine it a point out of all doubt from fifty places in your letters, were I to labour the proof,) if you would ingenuously own-",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Own what?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Why, my Anna Howe, I hope you don't think that I am already in love-!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "No, to be sure!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "How can your Anna Howe have such a thought?--What then shall we call it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "But, avoiding such hard names, let me tell you one thing, my dear (which nevertheless I have told you before); and that is this: that I shall think I have reason to be highly displeased with you, if, when you write to me, you endeavour to keep from me any secret of your heart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2526_156098_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2526/156098/2526_156098_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2526",
        "content": "Let me add, that if you would clearly and explicitly tell me, how far Lovelace has, or has not, a hold in your affections, I could better advise you what to do, than at present I can.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
